name: The Best Tire Ever
description: This is truly the apex of human kind. No tire in the history of man has ever reached such greatness. To those of you reading this i want you to truly ask yourself if something has ever been designed this good. Though this tire costed me a few fingers and countless hours of my life, it was all worth it. There have been many inventions throughout history that was more revolutionary than this tire. I used many human sacrifices but they were unimportant compared to the tire. all hail the mighty tire.
